		<title>05The Religion of Islam</title>
		<content> The five pillars of Islam are;        
 Faith in Allah                        
 Pray five times a day                 
 Giving of Alms (charity)              
 Keeping the fasts in the month of     
 Ramadon                               
 Making a pilgrimage to Mecca.         
 The Islamic calender consists of the  
 following months;                     
 1,    Muharram     2,  Safar          
 3, Rabi -al-Allival                   
 4,  Rabi-al-Thani                     
 5,Jamadi-al-Allival                   
 6, Jamadi-al-Thoni  7, Rajjab         
 8,  Shahban 9,  Romadan               
 10,  Shawal 11, Dhu-al-Qodah          
 12, Dhu-al-Hijah                      
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
